# 1. Copy this file to: application-local.properties (same folder)
# 2. Put secrets and machine-specific overrides only there (keep that file out of git if it contains secrets).
# 3. Run the backend with: --spring.profiles.active=local (optional; merges on top of application.properties)
#
# Base defaults (datasource, server.port, OAuth placeholders) live in application.properties.

